{
  "stem": "18061.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People came over in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, that what it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, you are released.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, you are supposed to be happy because they needed 6,000 people, and they got them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would not take any more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Fine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We gotten back to our little apartment, stayed there for couple of days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we thought some day, they-- it's the same thing, the Ukrainian and the Jewish police and the Polish and the Germans, they were still surrounded around.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that happened three days later on a Friday, the first day of [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Sohkot. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Another.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time we were from the same street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took us out, and we were sent to the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At the marketplace was a selection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you know what a selection is--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, selection is to select people to go to work or to go to debt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And mostly, what they-- mostly what they did is they're separated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For the Germans, which on top of them was this one [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dagenhardt. ?] I mentioned it before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They separated people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What that means is separate them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like they left a husband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took away the wife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Left the wife, they took away the-- the husband.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or they took away everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In my thing, when I came to the place where this selection was held, they didn't select nobody.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- they needed more people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went that time with my wife, my little brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My big brother with his wife and kid went already with the first aktion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother went with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my wife and my baby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- also was my wife's sister with her husband, also pregnant lady.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was in nine month.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For eight years she couldn't have a baby.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
